trans-unit.source: Custom columns : 'Description' and other custom columns you add by clicking on 'Add column' will not have their data overwritten. trans-unit.resname: Assembly['C is a constant offset. VEL is the velocity or slope or gradient of the straight line. ACC is the acceleration or coefficient of the second order. The function is a parabola.']

trans-unit.resname: Assembly['L1 is step level before time = T0. L2 is step level after time = T0. SLOPE defines the steepness of the transition between L1 and L2 about time = T0. Higher values gives sharper cornered steps. SLOPE = 1000 or greater are suitable.']
trans-unit.source: L1 is step level before time = T0. L2 is step level after time = T0. SLOPE defines the steepness of the transition between L1 and L2 about time = T0. Higher values gives sharper cornered steps. SLOPE = 1000 or greater are suitable.
trans-unit.target: L1 är stegnivån före tiden = T0. L2 är stegnivån efter tiden = T0. SLOPE definierar brantheten i övergången mellan L1 och L2 vid tiden = T0. Högre värden ger skarpare hörnsteg. SLOPE = 1000 eller högre är lämpliga.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly['H is the height of the impulse. T1 is the start of the impulse. T2 is the end of the impulse. SLOPE defines the steepness of the transition between 0 and H about time = T1 and T2. Higher values gives sharper cornered impulses. SLOPE = 1000 or greater are suitable.']
trans-unit.source: H is the height of the impulse. T1 is the start of the impulse. T2 is the end of the impulse. SLOPE defines the steepness of the transition between 0 and H about time = T1 and T2. Higher values gives sharper cornered impulses. SLOPE = 1000 or greater are suitable.
trans-unit.target: H är impulsens höjd. T1 är början på impulsen. T2 är slutet på impulsen. SLOPE definierar brantheten i övergången mellan 0 och H vid tiden = T1 och T2. Högre värden ger skarpare hörnimpulser. SLOPE = 1000 eller högre är lämpliga.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly['This is similar to the square impulse but the top has a sloping ramp. It is good for building a smooth piecewise linear function by adding a series of these. T1 is the start of the impulse. T2 is the end of the impulse. H1 is the height at T1 at the beginning of the ramp. H2 is the height at T2 at the end of the ramp. SLOPE defines the steepness of the transition between 0 and H1 and H2 to 0 about time = T1 and T2 respectively. Higher values gives sharper cornered impulses. SLOPE = 1000 or greater
trans-unit.source: This is similar to the square impulse but the top has a sloping ramp. It is good for building a smooth piecewise linear function by adding a series of these. T1 is the start of the impulse. T2 is the end of the impulse. H1 is the height at T1 at the beginning of the ramp. H2 is the height at T2 at the end of the ramp. SLOPE defines the steepness of the transition between 0 and H1 and H2 to 0 about time = T1 and T2 respectively. Higher values gives sharper cornered impulses. SLOPE = 1000 or greater are suitable.
trans-unit.target: Den här liknar den kvadratiska impulsen, men toppen har en sluttande ramp. Den är bra för att bygga en jämn styckvis linjär funktion genom att lägga till en serie av dessa. T1 är början på impulsen. T2 är slutet på impulsen. H1 är höjden vid T1 i början av rampen. H2 är höjden vid T2 i slutet av rampen. SLOPE definierar brantheten i övergången mellan 0 och H1 och H2 till 0 vid tid = T1 respektive T2. Högre värden ger skarpare hörnimpulser. SLOPE = 1000 eller högre är lämpliga.

trans-unit.resname: TaskAssemblyInsertLink['Sets whether the inserted sub-assemblies will be rigid or flexible. Rigid means that the added sub-assembly will be considered as a solid unit within the parent assembly. Flexible means that the added sub-assembly will allow movement of its individual components' joints within the parent assembly. You can change this behavior at any time by either right-clicking the sub-assembly on the document tree and toggling the 'Turn rigid'/'Turn flexible' command there, or by editing its Rigid
trans-unit.source: Sets whether the inserted sub-assemblies will be rigid or flexible. Rigid means that the added sub-assembly will be considered as a solid unit within the parent assembly. Flexible means that the added sub-assembly will allow movement of its individual components' joints within the parent assembly. You can change this behavior at any time by either right-clicking the sub-assembly on the document tree and toggling the 'Turn rigid'/'Turn flexible' command there, or by editing its Rigid property in the property editor.
trans-unit.target: Anger om de infogade underenheterna ska vara styva eller flexibla. Styv innebär att den underenhet som läggs till betraktas som en solid enhet i den överordnade enheten. Flexibel innebär att den tillagda underenheten tillåter rörelse av de enskilda komponenternas leder inom den överordnade enheten. Du kan ändra detta beteende när som helst genom att antingen högerklicka på underenheten i dokumentträdet och växla mellan "Turn rigid"/"Turn flexible" där, eller genom att redigera egenskapen Rigid i egenskapsredigeraren.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateBom['Creates a bill of materials of the current assembly. If an assembly is active, it will be a BOM of this assembly. Else it will be a BOM of the whole document.']
trans-unit.source: Creates a bill of materials of the current assembly. If an assembly is active, it will be a BOM of this assembly. Else it will be a BOM of the whole document.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en materialförteckning för den aktuella monteringen. Om en montering är aktiv kommer det att vara en stycklista för denna montering. Annars blir det en BOM för hela dokumentet.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateBom['The BOM object is a document object that stores the settings of your BOM. It is also a spreadsheet object so you can easily visualize the BOM. If you do not need the BOM object to be saved as a document object, you can simply export and cancel the task.']
trans-unit.source: The BOM object is a document object that stores the settings of your BOM. It is also a spreadsheet object so you can easily visualize the BOM. If you do not need the BOM object to be saved as a document object, you can simply export and cancel the task.
trans-unit.target: BOM-objektet är ett dokumentobjekt som lagrar inställningarna för din BOM. Det är också ett kalkylbladsobjekt så att du enkelt kan visualisera BOM. Om du inte vill att BOM-objektet ska sparas som ett dokumentobjekt kan du helt enkelt exportera och avbryta uppgiften.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateBom['The columns 'Index', 'Name', 'File Name' and 'Quantity' are automatically generated on recompute. The 'Description' and custom columns are not overwritten.']
trans-unit.source: The columns 'Index', 'Name', 'File Name' and 'Quantity' are automatically generated on recompute. The 'Description' and custom columns are not overwritten.
trans-unit.target: Kolumnerna "Index", "Name", "File Name" och "Quantity" genereras automatiskt vid omräkning. Kolumnerna 'Description' och 'Custom' skrivs inte över.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_InsertNewPart['Insert a new part into the active assembly. The new part's origin can be positioned in the assembly.']
trans-unit.source: Insert a new part into the active assembly. The new part's origin can be positioned in the assembly.
trans-unit.target: Infoga en ny del i den aktiva enheten. Den nya delens ursprung kan positioneras i enheten.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateAssembly['Creates an assembly object in the current document, or in the current active assembly (if any). Limit of one root assembly per file.']
trans-unit.source: Creates an assembly object in the current document, or in the current active assembly (if any). Limit of one root assembly per file.
trans-unit.target: Skapar ett monteringsobjekt i det aktuella dokumentet eller i den aktuella aktiva monteringen (om sådan finns). Begränsning till en rotmontering per fil.
trans-unit.note: why object? if obeject then write Assembly

trans-unit.target: Välj en enhet som ska aktiveras:

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_ActivateAssembly['Sets an assembly as the active one for editing.']
trans-unit.source: Sets an assembly as the active one for editing.
trans-unit.target: Anger en montering som aktiv för redigering.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointFixed['1 - If an assembly is active : Creates a joint permanently locking two parts together, preventing any movement or rotation']
trans-unit.source: 1 - If an assembly is active : Creates a joint permanently locking two parts together, preventing any movement or rotation
trans-unit.target: 1 - Om en montering är aktiv : Skapar en led som permanent låser ihop två delar och förhindrar all rörelse eller rotation

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointFixed['2 - If a part is active: Positions sub-parts by matching selected coordinate systems. The second part selected will move.']
trans-unit.source: 2 - If a part is active: Positions sub-parts by matching selected coordinate systems. The second part selected will move.
trans-unit.target: 2 - Om en del är aktiv: Positionerar underdelar genom att matcha valda koordinatsystem. Den andra valda delen kommer att flyttas.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointRevolute['Creates a revolute joint allowing rotation around a single axis between selected parts']
trans-unit.source: Creates a revolute joint allowing rotation around a single axis between selected parts
trans-unit.target: Skapar en revolverande led som möjliggör rotation runt en enda axel mellan valda delar

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointCylindrical['Creates a cylindrical joint that allows rotation around and translation along a single axis between assembled parts']
trans-unit.source: Creates a cylindrical joint that allows rotation around and translation along a single axis between assembled parts
trans-unit.target: Skapar en cylindrisk led som tillåter rotation runt och translation längs en enda axel mellan monterade delar

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointSlider['Creates a slider joint that allows linear movement along a single axis, but restricts rotation between selected parts']
trans-unit.source: Creates a slider joint that allows linear movement along a single axis, but restricts rotation between selected parts
trans-unit.target: Skapar en skjutled som tillåter linjär rörelse längs en enda axel, men begränsar rotationen mellan valda delar

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointBall['Creates a ball joint that connects parts at a point, allowing unrestricted movement as long as the connection points remain in contact']
trans-unit.source: Creates a ball joint that connects parts at a point, allowing unrestricted movement as long as the connection points remain in contact
trans-unit.target: Skapar en kulled som förbinder delar vid en punkt, vilket möjliggör obegränsad rörelse så länge anslutningspunkterna förblir i kontakt

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointDistance['Creates a distance joint that fixes the distance between the selected objects']
trans-unit.source: Creates a distance joint that fixes the distance between the selected objects
trans-unit.target: Skapar en avståndsled som fixerar avståndet mellan de markerade objekten

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointDistance['Creates one of several different joints based on the selectionFor example, a distance of 0 between a plane and a cylinder creates a tangent joint. A distance of 0 between planes will make them co-planar.']
trans-unit.source: Creates one of several different joints based on the selectionFor example, a distance of 0 between a plane and a cylinder creates a tangent joint. A distance of 0 between planes will make them co-planar.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en av flera olika fogar baserat på valetTill exempel skapar ett avstånd på 0 mellan ett plan och en cylinder en tangentfog. Ett avstånd på 0 mellan plan gör dem samplanära.
trans-unit.note:
the selectionFor example, a distance
reorganize this strings with return lines

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointParallel['Creates a parallel joint that makes the Z-axis of the selected coordinate systems parallel']
trans-unit.source: Creates a parallel joint that makes the Z-axis of the selected coordinate systems parallel
trans-unit.target: Skapar en parallell led som gör Z-axeln i de valda koordinatsystemen parallella

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointPerpendicular['Creates a perpendicular joint that makes the Z-axis of the selected coordinate systems perpendicular']
trans-unit.source: Creates a perpendicular joint that makes the Z-axis of the selected coordinate systems perpendicular
trans-unit.target: Skapar en vinkelrät led som gör Z-axeln i de valda koordinatsystemen vinkelräta

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointAngle['Creates an angle joint that fixes the angle between the Z-axis of the selected coordinate systems']
trans-unit.source: Creates an angle joint that fixes the angle between the Z-axis of the selected coordinate systems
trans-unit.target: Skapar en vinkelfog som fixerar vinkeln mellan Z-axeln i de valda koordinatsystemen

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointRackPinion['Creates a rack and pinion joint that links a part with a sliding joint to a part with a revolute joint']
trans-unit.source: Creates a rack and pinion joint that links a part with a sliding joint to a part with a revolute joint
trans-unit.target: Skapar en kuggstångsled som kopplar en del med en glidande led till en del med en roterande led

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointRackPinion['Selects the same coordinate systems as the revolute and sliding joints. The pitch radius defines the movement ratio between the rack and the pinion.']
trans-unit.source: Selects the same coordinate systems as the revolute and sliding joints. The pitch radius defines the movement ratio between the rack and the pinion.
trans-unit.target: Väljer samma koordinatsystem som revolver- och glidlederna. Delningsradien definierar rörelseförhållandet mellan kuggstången och pinnen.
trans-unit.note: In this case it is an instruction for the user and should start with an imperative: Select

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointGears['Creates a gears joint that links 2 rotating gears together. They will have inverse rotation direction.']
trans-unit.source: Creates a gears joint that links 2 rotating gears together. They will have inverse rotation direction.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en kugghjulslänk som kopplar ihop 2 roterande kugghjul. De kommer att ha omvänd rotationsriktning.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_CreateJointBelt['Creates a belt joint that links 2 rotating objects together. They will have the same rotation direction.']
trans-unit.source: Creates a belt joint that links 2 rotating objects together. They will have the same rotation direction.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en remled som kopplar ihop 2 roterande objekt. De kommer att ha samma rotationsriktning.

trans-unit.resname: Assembly_ToggleGrounded['Toggles the grounding of a part. Grounding a part permanently locks its position in the assembly, preventing any movement or rotation. You need at least one grounded part before starting to assemble.']
trans-unit.source: Toggles the grounding of a part. Grounding a part permanently locks its position in the assembly, preventing any movement or rotation. You need at least one grounded part before starting to assemble.
trans-unit.target: Växlar jordningen av en del. Genom att jorda en del låses dess position permanent i monteringen, vilket förhindrar all rörelse eller rotation. Du behöver minst en jordad del innan du börjar montera.

trans-unit.target: Skapar en ny simulering av den aktuella monteringen
